column2: If there was a diamond on a green wall there would not be one on the purple side. Where walls did not match there was never a diamond. In the blank rooms if there was a colored corner then that is th color of the wall where the diamond would be.

column1: On the larger maps the movement performance was TERRIBLE when turning. There was very jerky motion and then suddenly fast motion while turning. It was bad enough that I had to take a break to keep from getting motion sickness from the horrible inconsistency with the motion while turning. It is not a problem with my computer
column2: I have a 6 core CPU and an AMD graphics card.
